Win32-xul2ppt_mec version 0.01
==============================

This is to convert .xul files to .ppt files with virtual or mechanical method.
By controlling keys and mouse automacally, you can convert your .xul 
to ppt in your free time.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Win32::Guitest
Clipboard
Carp

And if you need to trim the pictures to get a mini-ppt files 
Image-Magic installer also prerequired.

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


